231
00:15:22,352 --> 00:15:25,352
There's no way she
wouldn't have recognized me.

232
00:15:26,122 --> 00:15:28,222
That would explain everything.

233
00:15:29,652 --> 00:15:31,368
If she was after his
money from the start...

234
00:15:31,392 --> 00:15:32,822
